 Nifaq: Only believers fear committing acts of hypocrisy","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 5, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn al-Qayyim reported: Hasan al-Basri, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cNo one fears hypocrisy but a believer. No one feels safe from hypocrisy but a hypocrite.\u201d Source: al-Jawa\u0304b al-Ka\u0304fi\u0304 1\/42 \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0628\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u0642\u064a\u0645 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062d\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0646\u0650\u00a0\u0642\u0627\u0644 \u0631\u062d\u0645\u0647 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0645\u064e\u0627 \u062e\u064e\u0627\u0641\u064e\u0647\u064f (\u0627\u0644\u0646\u0641\u0627\u0642) \u0625\u0650\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0627 \u0645\u064f\u0624\u0652\u0645\u0650\u0646\u064c \u0648\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0627 \u0623\u064e\u0645\u0650\u0646\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0625\u0650\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0627 \u0645\u064f\u0646\u064e\u0627\u0641\u0650\u0642\u064c 1\/42 \u0627\u0644\u062c\u0648\u0627\u0628\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":42020,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2024\/07\/22\/abu-darda-we-know\/","url_meta":{"origin":25336,"position":3},"title":"Abu Darda on Muslims: We know who is wicked or righteous","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 22, 2024","format":false,"excerpt":"Jubayr ibn Nufayr reported: Abu Darda, may Allah be pleased with him, used to say about people, \u201cWe know you better than a veterinarian knows his animals. We surely know the best of you from the worst of you. As for the best of you, goodness is expected from them\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062